{"tid":1045034,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚同囡囡睇皇馬俾佢笑我","createTime":"2019-03-03T10:32:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T22:14:22.000Z","uid":58811,"like":13,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"72cd0588d483b1ff885e18ca159e5db325046e8d","tid":1045034,"uid":58811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T10:32:22.000Z","msg":"琴晚同條囡睇波！<br />\n條囡原本話3點9唔能睇！<br />\n我勸佢話有c朗同皇馬3連西甲冠軍好能勁佢先肯！<br />\n唉但我屌佢老味，點知皇馬輸波！俾我條囡笑我捧對渣波，又問我點解C朗隱咗形，又問我點解西甲無VAR咁落後！<br />\n而家仲𥄫到條囡同公司條死疤狗whatsapp緊！<br />\n唉谷鳩氣！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"996a6d7d5ce003371e98d81f5bb229dab868e80b","tid":1045034,"uid":58811,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T10:35:46.000Z","msg":"利伸廿年皇馬球迷<br />\nHaha Madrid"},{"pid":"0f9cc1ddd695bfa44fcbfa8a7e28de832fa80a96","tid":1045034,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T11:17:15.000Z","msg":"我都想渣波"},{"pid":"318979c63aabf26bbd55a51339ab6aef808aa30e","tid":1045034,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T11:18:33.000Z","msg":"樓主a0"},{"pid":"f6829b01f6ad2fa47e3d750d0c98daa520f8b852","tid":1045034,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"318979c63aabf26bbd55a51339ab6aef808aa30e","tid":1045034,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T11:18:33.000Z","msg":"樓主a0"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T11:20:45.000Z","msg":"佢同小妹拍緊拖"},{"pid":"fac440caadaab20bab7bae1f568256c5e79aedb7","tid":1045034,"uid":58811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"318979c63aabf26bbd55a51339ab6aef808aa30e","tid":1045034,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T11:18:33.000Z","msg":"樓主a0"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T11:43:50.000Z","msg":"我A09"},{"pid":"f197b4560f810c005f35efb63640f28fb289ce47","tid":1045034,"uid":58811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6829b01f6ad2fa47e3d750d0c98d